WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:07.424 --> 00:00:11.761
There's a lonely vintage
Aching in my chest…

2
00:00:11.845 --> 00:00:15.015
Love. it's a feeling
that lets me know that she's the one.

3
00:00:15.098 --> 00:00:17.392
You ain't in my sight line

4
00:00:17.475 --> 00:00:20.478
I'm very ready for marriage.
That's my M.O.

5
00:00:20.562 --> 00:00:22.272
Ride or die. my wife for life.

6
00:00:22.856 --> 00:00:25.025
He's my soulmate.
I love him with all my heart.

7
00:00:25.108 --> 00:00:26.901
But he isn't ready to get married.

8
00:00:26.985 --> 00:00:29.738
It's been four years.
Like. marry me or move on.

9
00:00:30.321 --> 00:00:33.158
Could give me everything
But it ain't enough…

10
00:00:33.241 --> 00:00:34.451
There's a lot at stake.

11
00:00:34.534 --> 00:00:36.453
We're really putting
our relationship on the line.

12
00:00:36.536 --> 00:00:39.581
I definitely don't want to lose her.
but is the grass greener?

13
00:00:39.664 --> 00:00:41.541
I'm curious to figure it out.

14
00:00:41.624 --> 00:00:43.126
Gonna have a good time. good time…

15
00:00:43.209 --> 00:00:45.587
-Do you kiss with eyes open or closed?
-Closed.

16
00:00:45.670 --> 00:00:49.090
It is insane
that I'm dating five other guys.

17
00:00:49.174 --> 00:00:50.967
Go!

18
00:00:51.051 --> 00:00:52.969
Choosing her is a really big decision

19
00:00:53.053 --> 00:00:55.430
that would change
the course of my life forever.

20
00:00:55.513 --> 00:00:56.347
Thank you.

21
00:00:56.431 --> 00:01:00.769
Someone I met a week ago
is fulfilling the needs that I'm missing.

22
00:01:00.852 --> 00:01:03.021
Is it scary? Absolutely.

23
00:01:03.104 --> 00:01:04.731
You're looking real good tonight. baby.

24
00:01:04.814 --> 00:01:07.776
Coming to this experience.
I'm the one that needs to seek answers.

25
00:01:07.859 --> 00:01:09.110
-We look good together.
-Yeah.

26
00:01:09.194 --> 00:01:11.071
I'm ready to get married.

27
00:01:11.154 --> 00:01:13.531
and I'm looking for someone
who's ready now.

28
00:01:13.615 --> 00:01:15.992
-You're in my frickin' head.
-Oh. we are sharing a brain cell.

29
00:01:16.076 --> 00:01:18.620
To our trial marriage.

30
00:01:18.703 --> 00:01:20.872
Sun's out. buns out?

31
00:01:20.955 --> 00:01:22.332
-Yeah.
-All right.

32
00:01:22.415 --> 00:01:24.375
I can see myself
marrying someone like Monica.

33
00:01:24.459 --> 00:01:26.586
You want to make out or what?

34
00:01:26.669 --> 00:01:30.173
I'll figure out if we're not supposed to
spend the rest of our lives together.

35
00:01:30.256 --> 00:01:32.300
We could not leave here together.

36
00:01:32.801 --> 00:01:34.969
There's something that did happen.
you know?

37
00:01:35.053 --> 00:01:37.764
In all fairness.
I need that physical intimacy.

38
00:01:38.348 --> 00:01:40.975
Shit is about to go down.

39
00:01:41.976 --> 00:01:45.647
His manipulative behavior is disgusting.
It's appalling.

40
00:01:47.649 --> 00:01:50.068
If you love me.
why are you saying those things?

41
00:01:50.151 --> 00:01:53.321
You straight-up lied to my face.
over and over and over!

42
00:01:53.404 --> 00:01:56.741
-Shut the fuck up and listen to me!
-Stop talking to her like that.

43
00:01:57.408 --> 00:01:59.702
I'm questioning
everything about our relationship.

44
00:01:59.786 --> 00:02:02.038
I am going to defend myself. period.

45
00:02:02.122 --> 00:02:03.706
Damage has been done.

46
00:02:06.084 --> 00:02:09.963
This needs to be a massive wake-up call.
You should never be spoken to that way.

47
00:02:11.673 --> 00:02:12.549
Wow.

48
00:02:12.632 --> 00:02:15.009
We're gonna ask you
to leave the experience.

49
00:02:15.093 --> 00:02:17.512
I'm so ready to be done with this.

50
00:02:17.595 --> 00:02:20.306
There's an obvious risk
issuing the Ultimatum.

51
00:02:20.390 --> 00:02:22.350
but in my opinion. it's worth it.

52
00:02:22.433 --> 00:02:24.811
I'll get the answers I need.

53
00:02:24.894 --> 00:02:27.188
Can't put a price on the human touch…

54
00:02:27.272 --> 00:02:29.482
I am giving my boyfriend an Ultimatum.

55
00:02:29.566 --> 00:02:33.236
If he does not want to get married.
I got to go.

56
00:02:33.319 --> 00:02:34.654
-Hi.
-Hi.

57
00:02:34.737 --> 00:02:36.030
Ashley. nice to meet you.

58
00:02:36.114 --> 00:02:37.157
-David.
-David?

59
00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:38.700
-Hello.
-Hi!

60
00:02:38.783 --> 00:02:40.910
-Good evening. guys.
-Hi. everyone.

61
00:02:40.994 --> 00:02:42.871
-How is everybody?
-Welcome.

62
00:02:42.954 --> 00:02:44.414
I'm Vanessa Lachey.

63
00:02:44.497 --> 00:02:45.623
I'm Nick Lachey.

64
00:02:45.707 --> 00:02:48.042
And this is The Ultimatum.

65
00:02:48.126 --> 00:02:52.839
You love me to Heaven
Love me to Heaven. babe

66
00:02:53.840 --> 00:02:56.050
-Welcome. guys.
-Yeah!

67
00:02:56.134 --> 00:02:59.179
Each of you have arrived here
as part of a couple.

68
00:02:59.262 --> 00:03:02.432
Someone in the relationship
has issued an Ultimatum.

69
00:03:03.391 --> 00:03:06.060
One of you is ready to be married.

70
00:03:06.144 --> 00:03:10.481
and the other one is not so ready… yet.

71
00:03:10.565 --> 00:03:11.941
Show of hands.

72
00:03:12.025 --> 00:03:14.152
Who here is receiving the Ultimatum?

73
00:03:18.114 --> 00:03:20.200
Jessica Grace. the time is now.

74
00:03:20.283 --> 00:03:22.410
-It was yesterday.
-Yesterday?

75
00:03:24.454 --> 00:03:30.418
We both want kids. and for me.
marriage has to come before that.

76
00:03:30.501 --> 00:03:33.963
And when I think about
my dad's health being what it is.

77
00:03:34.047 --> 00:03:36.549
I definitely want him to be around
for some of those big moments.

78
00:03:36.633 --> 00:03:39.302
Again. time is of the essence.

79
00:03:40.386 --> 00:03:42.847
You know.
I have three promise rings from him.

80
00:03:42.931 --> 00:03:46.976
And I told him. the last promise ring.
I was running out of finger space. so…

81
00:03:48.519 --> 00:03:51.731
David. three promise rings.

82
00:03:51.814 --> 00:03:54.275
Just promise to love her forever.
you know?

83
00:03:54.359 --> 00:03:56.778
Promise to be her man and just. you know.

84
00:03:56.861 --> 00:03:59.405
take care of her.
provide for her. protect her.

85
00:03:59.489 --> 00:04:00.323
Three times.

86
00:04:00.406 --> 00:04:02.700
Three times. Hey. gotta remind her.

87
00:04:02.784 --> 00:04:05.370
-Reassuring.
-Reassuring.

88
00:04:05.453 --> 00:04:07.163
Monica. what do you think it is

89
00:04:07.247 --> 00:04:10.959
that's holding you up
from taking this leap of faith with him?

90
00:04:11.042 --> 00:04:16.589
For me. there's certain steps in my mind
that I need to take before I marry.

91
00:04:16.673 --> 00:04:20.593
That's having my career in line.
my finances in line.

92
00:04:20.677 --> 00:04:23.304
Because if I'm being honest.
I'm a high-maintenance girly.

93
00:04:23.388 --> 00:04:25.848
I have a lot that I want out of life.

94
00:04:26.599 --> 00:04:29.602
I first met Monica when I was 14.

95
00:04:29.686 --> 00:04:31.271
She lived down the street from me.

96
00:04:31.354 --> 00:04:34.899
And then it was during COVID
when we re-met.

97
00:04:34.983 --> 00:04:38.152
And I was just blown away.
I had that movie moment.

98
00:04:38.236 --> 00:04:39.362
The lights came down.

99
00:04:39.445 --> 00:04:41.823
her hair blew in the wind.
and I was shell-shocked.

100
00:04:41.906 --> 00:04:45.285
I told her.
"You get prettier every time I see you."

101
00:04:45.368 --> 00:04:47.245
She friend-zoned me for a while.

102
00:04:47.829 --> 00:04:51.582
He's the lover boy.
He's the romantic one. He knew right away.

103
00:04:51.666 --> 00:04:53.626
Our connection is unreal.

104
00:04:53.710 --> 00:04:56.004
I truly believe I would die without her.

105
00:04:57.964 --> 00:05:03.428
To me. marriage means more
than just being in love with somebody.

106
00:05:03.511 --> 00:05:04.762
I'm not the type of person

107
00:05:04.846 --> 00:05:07.307
to just fall in love
and then run to the altar.

108
00:05:08.641 --> 00:05:13.021
All of you are about to have
a once-in-a-lifetime experience.

109
00:05:13.104 --> 00:05:16.274
And in that experience.
you'll explore two different versions

110
00:05:16.357 --> 00:05:19.444
of what your married life could be like.

111
00:05:19.527 --> 00:05:22.655
And if you're still not ready
to marry your current partner.

112
00:05:22.739 --> 00:05:25.533
chances are they may find
someone else who is.

113
00:05:27.994 --> 00:05:28.911
Blake.

114
00:05:28.995 --> 00:05:32.290
you've given Hayley
the Ultimatum. correct?

115
00:05:32.373 --> 00:05:33.499
I have.

116
00:05:33.583 --> 00:05:35.835
I feel like I'm ready for marriage now.

117
00:05:35.918 --> 00:05:37.628
I've had the opportunity

118
00:05:37.712 --> 00:05:40.715
to check a couple personal items
off my bucket list.

119
00:05:40.798 --> 00:05:42.884
And I think that's the next logical step.

120
00:05:43.468 --> 00:05:45.928
One of my goals is to have a.
you know. big family.

121
00:05:46.012 --> 00:05:48.222
You know. a family of five.

122
00:05:48.306 --> 00:05:50.767
Like. five. six max.

123
00:05:50.850 --> 00:05:55.355
But Blake and I are kind of fire and ice
because Blake's very practical.

124
00:05:55.438 --> 00:05:57.190
I'm spicy.

125
00:05:57.273 --> 00:06:00.318
-And Blake's like. ugh.
-My favorite is when hands start to clap.

126
00:06:00.401 --> 00:06:03.571
Absolutely not.
Or. like. something like that. Yeah.

127
00:06:04.197 --> 00:06:06.574
Blake is amazing.
and he has so much to offer.

128
00:06:06.657 --> 00:06:10.161
But whenever it comes
to my emotional needs.

129
00:06:10.244 --> 00:06:12.163
some things aren't being met.

130
00:06:12.246 --> 00:06:16.000
I've discussed this many times.
and it's not being fixed.

131
00:06:16.584 --> 00:06:20.963
That's why I'm not just ready
to jump right into marriage.

132
00:06:21.047 --> 00:06:25.134
Blake. would you say you'd be willing
to walk away if she says no?

133
00:06:25.218 --> 00:06:27.053
I think that after this experience.

134
00:06:27.136 --> 00:06:30.640
if you don't have a clear answer as to
what you want out of our relationship.

135
00:06:30.723 --> 00:06:31.891
I'd have to walk away.

136
00:06:34.435 --> 00:06:37.313
Ashley. you issued
the Ultimatum to Killian.

137
00:06:37.397 --> 00:06:41.192
Yes. I'm a Southern Texas girl.

138
00:06:41.275 --> 00:06:47.323
I grew up. everyone gets married. engaged.
has kids right out of high school.

139
00:06:47.407 --> 00:06:49.534
and I was just raised that way.

140
00:06:49.617 --> 00:06:51.244
I want a family of my own.

141
00:06:51.327 --> 00:06:54.705
I mean. we've known each other
for over 14 years now.

142
00:06:54.789 --> 00:06:57.208
We met through competitive cheerleading.

143
00:06:57.291 --> 00:06:59.168
I had a little crush on Killian.

144
00:06:59.252 --> 00:07:03.589
so I'd. uh. post him
as my Man Crush Monday.

145
00:07:03.673 --> 00:07:07.135
It was a thing in cheerleading
to take. like. kissing pictures together.

146
00:07:07.218 --> 00:07:10.388
-She forced me to.
-No. he wanted to.

147
00:07:11.681 --> 00:07:14.934
We've lived together for four years.
We have two dogs together.

148
00:07:15.017 --> 00:07:17.186
Our entire lives are like co-mingled.

149
00:07:17.270 --> 00:07:21.649
I just can't continue
if he's not on the same page as I am.

150
00:07:21.732 --> 00:07:25.027
He was at some point ready.

151
00:07:25.111 --> 00:07:28.531
He actually asked my dad for my hand.

152
00:07:28.614 --> 00:07:31.492
So it's kind of confusing because

153
00:07:31.576 --> 00:07:34.120
why were you ready at some point.
but now you're not?

154
00:07:36.164 --> 00:07:41.419
We just had a family altercation
between her father and I.

155
00:07:41.502 --> 00:07:45.047
And it upset him.
and it started to make me think.

156
00:07:45.131 --> 00:07:50.428
"Is this something that would happen
down the road consistently?"

157
00:07:51.012 --> 00:07:53.139
My family is super close-knit.

158
00:07:53.222 --> 00:07:54.849
I'm daddy's little girl.

159
00:07:54.932 --> 00:07:57.351
You know I've always wanted a big family.

160
00:07:57.435 --> 00:07:59.896
or I like being around
big families like yours.

161
00:07:59.979 --> 00:08:03.191
But are we gonna have
to have our own separate life

162
00:08:03.274 --> 00:08:07.195
just due to not knowing
if her family truly accepts me for me?

163
00:08:08.571 --> 00:08:10.323
It's tricky. those dynamics.

164
00:08:10.406 --> 00:08:13.034
because you're not just marrying
the person with you.

165
00:08:13.117 --> 00:08:16.078
You're marrying into their family.
and they into yours.

166
00:08:16.162 --> 00:08:17.788
-Oh. he knows.
-Those are all stresses.

167
00:08:17.872 --> 00:08:19.999
Those emotions are all very. very real.

168
00:08:20.875 --> 00:08:23.669
Tonight is your last night
together as a couple.

169
00:08:23.753 --> 00:08:27.215
Tomorrow. you will accept the Ultimatum.

170
00:08:27.298 --> 00:08:29.800
You will break up.
and you will become exes.

171
00:08:29.884 --> 00:08:33.012
You will date
each of your new potential partners

172
00:08:33.095 --> 00:08:34.597
who are standing right here.

173
00:08:34.680 --> 00:08:38.351
And in one week.
you'll all be back here for The Choice.

174
00:08:38.434 --> 00:08:42.021
You'll each choose a partner
who you think has all of the qualities

175
00:08:42.104 --> 00:08:44.941
that you see in your spouse.

176
00:08:45.024 --> 00:08:47.818
You'll move in together
for a three-week Trial Marriage.

177
00:08:47.902 --> 00:08:51.405
And then you'll do it all over again

178
00:08:51.489 --> 00:08:54.492
with the person
you're standing next to right now.

179
00:08:55.159 --> 00:08:58.538
At the end of this.
you'll leave here either engaged.

180
00:08:58.621 --> 00:08:59.580
alone.

181
00:08:59.664 --> 00:09:02.583
or possibly in love with someone new.

182
00:09:04.001 --> 00:09:08.089
An engagement ring is a traditional sign
of your commitment to marriage.

183
00:09:08.172 --> 00:09:11.008
We are providing
a selection of engagement rings

184
00:09:11.092 --> 00:09:15.513
that you may use if you choose to propose
when the Ultimatum comes to term.

185
00:09:15.596 --> 00:09:17.682
You know what I want.

186
00:09:17.765 --> 00:09:20.643
-They're all the same size.
-No fighting.

187
00:09:20.726 --> 00:09:23.437
Choosing someone to commit to life with

188
00:09:23.521 --> 00:09:26.399
is one of the biggest decisions
that you will ever make.

189
00:09:26.482 --> 00:09:29.235
Ultimately. we want you
to make the right decision.

190
00:09:29.318 --> 00:09:31.028
but with the right person.

191
00:09:31.696 --> 00:09:34.115
We will see you all again in one week

192
00:09:34.198 --> 00:09:37.493
for a very important decision
at The Choice.

193
00:09:37.577 --> 00:09:39.245
Until then. cheers to love. guys.

194
00:09:39.328 --> 00:09:41.581
Cheers to love.

195
00:09:41.664 --> 00:09:42.915
You got one life. so own it

196
00:09:42.999 --> 00:09:45.167
You gotta seize the day
This is your moment…

197
00:09:45.251 --> 00:09:47.670
-There we go. Come on.
-Let's do it.

198
00:09:47.753 --> 00:09:49.839
I love Jessica as much as I possibly can.

199
00:09:49.922 --> 00:09:53.884
but. like. this experience
doesn't come without having risks.

200
00:09:53.968 --> 00:09:55.469
There is possibilities out there.

201
00:09:56.053 --> 00:09:59.599
Ashley. she's got assets
from a physical standpoint.

202
00:09:59.682 --> 00:10:02.018
She's gifted in that sense.

203
00:10:02.602 --> 00:10:05.938
While she's like. um…
Hold on. let me gather myself here.

204
00:10:07.106 --> 00:10:08.816
I try to keep my eyes up.

205
00:10:09.567 --> 00:10:12.486
But yeah. I notice she's got a bosom.

206
00:10:12.570 --> 00:10:16.073
Come on. come on. come on. come on
It's all up to you…

207
00:10:16.157 --> 00:10:17.658
Man. this is crazy.

208
00:10:17.742 --> 00:10:18.868
This is wild.

209
00:10:18.951 --> 00:10:23.664
If I'm being completely honest.
it feels scary to receive an Ultimatum.

210
00:10:23.748 --> 00:10:27.209
I'm head over heels in love with Lucas.
but I have always wondered.

211
00:10:27.293 --> 00:10:29.337
is the grass maybe greener
on the other side?

212
00:10:29.420 --> 00:10:32.214
If I had somebody
that was a little bit more like me.

213
00:10:32.298 --> 00:10:35.009
how we would do together in a marriage?

214
00:10:35.092 --> 00:10:37.428
So it's something
I am constantly thinking about.

215
00:10:37.511 --> 00:10:39.138
Good life. good life

216
00:10:39.221 --> 00:10:41.349
La-la. da-da-da

217
00:10:41.432 --> 00:10:43.601
You know the time now
We're going all out

218
00:10:43.684 --> 00:10:45.770
We're gonna show the world
What you're all about

219
00:10:45.853 --> 00:10:49.273
Just good. good. good. good vibes

220
00:10:49.357 --> 00:10:51.359
Welcome to the good life

221
00:10:51.442 --> 00:10:53.986
-Do you want to see something?
-Yeah. what you got?

222
00:10:54.070 --> 00:10:55.655
-Look at that.
-That's pretty.

223
00:10:55.738 --> 00:10:57.657
-It does fit.
-It does.

224
00:10:57.740 --> 00:10:59.450
Look. with all the promise rings.

225
00:10:59.533 --> 00:11:01.494
Wow. that is…

226
00:11:01.577 --> 00:11:03.788
It just kind of cramps
the promise ring style though.

227
00:11:03.871 --> 00:11:07.541
Oh my gosh. you're obnoxious.

228
00:11:09.043 --> 00:11:10.711
You know why I'm not ready. right?

229
00:11:12.254 --> 00:11:13.464
Yeah.

230
00:11:13.547 --> 00:11:17.968
It takes time to get
where I'm able to just fully commit

231
00:11:18.052 --> 00:11:20.680
and just lose that fear
of you leaving one day.

232
00:11:20.763 --> 00:11:21.639
you know what I mean?

233
00:11:21.722 --> 00:11:24.433
You think seeing me with someone
and then picking you in the end

234
00:11:24.517 --> 00:11:27.144
would help you remove that fear?

235
00:11:27.645 --> 00:11:30.231
I don't know.
I don't even want to think about that now.

236
00:11:30.314 --> 00:11:32.274
It's nothing to do with you.
You know what I mean?

237
00:11:32.358 --> 00:11:33.609
-Mm-hm.
-It's how I was raised.

238
00:11:33.693 --> 00:11:37.697
It's tough not being able
to see a happy marriage at all.

239
00:11:37.780 --> 00:11:40.950
But. you know. I still have hope.
Always have hope.

240
00:11:41.033 --> 00:11:43.869
You bring light to everything. so…

241
